Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be performed after SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time for SW-EIC Reject across all process variants ending with this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-EIC Reject and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of SW-EIC Reject in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurred at least once
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-EIC Reject' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-EIC Reject in the variant with the longest overall duration
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-AE Recommendation overdue and SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Recommendation overdue' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be done after the final SW-Reviewer Agreed in a case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time between the last occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-EIC Reject following SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants that originated from a checklist completion path
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-EIC Reject in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed appears exactly once
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time between SW-Reviewer Selection is now due and SW-EIC Reject in high-complexity reviewer assignment variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Cycle Time of SW-EIC Reject measured from the moment the manuscript enters SW-Awaiting EIC Decision until the rejection decision is logged
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time to SW-EIC Reject grouped by case:concept:name in traces containing both SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'
